The Kid Stays in the Picture;;80;;91;;R;;Traces the meteoric rise, fall, and rise again of legendary Hollywood producer Robert Evans. Adapted from Mr. Evans's tell-all autobiography, the movie takes the audience on an intimate journey into the mind of this Hollywood legend. "The Kid Stays in the Picture" shares gripping anecdotes about Evans's unusual friendships and follows the thread of his tumultuous love life.;;Documentary;;Nanette Burstein,Brett Morgen;;2002;;Robert Evans;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kid_stays_in_the_picture